Step 1: Install yoeunes/toastr package
$ composer require yoeunes/toastr
'providers' => [
    ...
    Yoeunes\Toastr\ToastrServiceProvider::class
    ...
];
php artisan vendor:publish --provider='Yoeunes\Toastr\ToastrServiceProvider'
Step 2: Create View
